===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|ametist}}, from {{der|en|fro|ametiste}} ({{cog|fr|améthyste}}), from {{der|en|grc|ἀμέθυστος||not drunk}}, from {{m|grc|ἀ-||not}} + {{m|grc|μεθύω||I am drunk}}, from {{m|grc|μέθυ||wine}}. The Greeks believed that the amethyst prevented [[intoxication]].

